Changelog:

2017-04-10
-  Version 1.0.1
 - Added Russian language
 - Fix css to make reCAPTCHA dialog centered

2015-05-12:
 - Version 1.0.0
 - Switched to new "No CAPTCHA reCAPTCHA" (see http://goo.gl/eX85TW)

2015-05-12:
 - Version 1.0.0
 - Switched to new "No CAPTCHA reCAPTCHA" (see http://goo.gl/eX85TW)

2014-01-26:
 - Version 0.9.9
 - Updated to use google.com URLs
 - Using the SSL reCAPTCHA URLs by default to fix mixed-mode issues on SSL
   websites.

2011-06-30:
 - Updated key creation URL
 - Added Spanish language
 - Added German language
 - Fixed styles other than "Clean" displaying with left alignment

2011-06-18:
 - Version 0.9.8a
 - Updated reCAPTCHA library
 - Marked as compatible with SMF 2.0

2010-03-13:
 - Version 0.9.8
 - Updated to work with 2.0 RC3
 - Fixed display issue with 2.0 RC3

2009-11-14:
 - Version 0.9.7
 - Updated to work with 2.0 RC2 and Curve
 - Dropped support for 2.0 pre-release versions older than RC2

2009-07-19:
 - Version 0.9.6
 - Updated to indicate support for 2.0 RC1.2

2009-07-05:
 - Fixed validation errors on SMF 1.1 series and old tabled Core for early SMF
   2.0 betas
 - Hopefully removed all the undefined indexes in the code

2009-02-19:
 - Version 0.9.5.4b
 - Updated to install on 2.0 RC1-1

2009-02-19:
 - Version 0.9.5.4a
 - Updated to install directly on 2.0 RC1

2008-12-27
 - Version 0.9.5.4
 - Fixed bug causing undefined index errors (BT #19)
 - Fixed mis-named variables
 - Small code cleanup for 2.0b3 and newer
 - Updated README to include 2.0 setting location

2008-09-17
 - Version 0.9.5.3
 - Updated to support all 1.1 sub-versions. It doesn't look like there will be
   major changes in the affected areas.
 - Updated for SMF 2.0 Beta 4

2008-07-18
 - Version 0.9.5.2
 - Added support for SMF 2.0 Beta 3 and 3.1. As a result, we now fully replace
   the traditional visual verification when enabled.

2008-05-20
 - Version 0.9.5.1
 - Fixed to support SMF 1.1.5

2008-02-09
 - Version 0.9.5
 - Fixed issue with non-JavaScript reCAPTCHA display
 - Added British English, and UTF-8 support for English and British English
 - Added support for 2.0 Beta 1, Beta 1.1, Beta 2, Beta 2.1

2007-12-27
 - Version 0.9
 - Initial Release
